quran[8{c,v,t}:
2,30,"phir zara is waqt ka tasawwur karo jab tumahray Rab ne firshton se kaha tha ke"" Mein zameen mein aik khalifa bananay wala hon"" unhon ne arz kya :"" kya Aap zameen mein kisi aisay ko muqarar karne walay hain, jo is ke intizam ko bigaar day ga aur khonraziyan kere ga Aap ki hamd o Sana ke sath tasbeeh aur Aap ke liye taqdees to hum kar hi rahay hain"" farmaya :"" Mein jaanta hon jo kuch tum nahi jantay """
2,31,"is ke baad Allah ne Aadam ko saari cheezon ke naam sikhayiye, phir inhen firshton ke samnay paish kya aur farmaya"" agar tumhara khayaal sahih hai ( ke kisi khalifa ke taqarrur se intizam baggar jaye ga ) to zara un cheezon ke naam batao """
2,32,"unhon ne arz kya :"" nuqs se pak to Aap hi ki zaat hai, hum to bas itna hi ilm rakhtay hain, jitna Aap ne hum ko day diya hai haqeeqat mein sab kuch jan-nay aur samajhney wala Aap ke siwa koi nahi """
2,33,"phir Allah ne Aadam se kaha :"" tum iِnhain inn cheezon ke naam batao"" jab is ne un ko unn sab ke naam bta diye, to Allah ne farmaya :"" Mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke mein asmano aur zameen ki woh saari haqeqteen jaanta hon jo tum se makhfi hain, jo kuch tum zahir karte ho, woh bhi mujhe maloom hai aur jo kuch tum chupatay ho, usay bhi mein jaanta hon """
2,34,"phir jab hum ne firshton ko hukum diya ke Aadam ke agay jhuk jao, to sab jhuk gay, magar iblees ne inkaar kya woh apni barayi ke ghamand mein par gaya aur na farmanoon mein shaamil ho gaya"
2,35,"phir hum ne Aadam se kaha ke"" tum aur tumhari biwi, dono jannat mein raho aur yahan bafraghatjo chaho khao, magar is darakht ka rukh nah karna, warna zaalmon mein shumaar ho ge """
2,36,"aakhir-kaar shetan ne un dono ko is darakht ki targheeb day kar hamaray hukum ki pairwi se hataa diya aur inhen uss haalat se nikalwa kar chorra, jis mein woh thay hum ne hukum diya ke,"" ab tum sab yahan se utar jao, tum aik dosray ke dushman ho aur tumhe aik khaas waqt taq zameen par therana thehrnaaur wahein guzar busr karna hai """
2,37,"is waqt Aadam ne apne Rab se chund kalmaat seekh kar tauba ki, jis ko is ke Rab ne qubool kar liya, kyunkay woh bara maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
